OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid vaccines: Children   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftold to delay jab for 12   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fweeks after infection      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Healthy children aged 12 to 17 are     
OL,6, being advised to wait 12 weeks after a 
OL,7, coronavirus infection before having a  
OL,8, Covid jab in the UK.                   
OL,10,FPreviously the advice was to leave a   
OL,11,Ffour-week gap.                         
OL,13,FThe UK Health Security Agency said the 
OL,14,Fchange was a precaution against the    
OL,15,Fsmall risk of heart inflammation.      
OL,17,FUK vaccine advisers recommended a      
OL,18,F12-week gap between doses when they    
OL,19,Fgave a green light on Monday for 16 and
OL,20,F17-year-olds to get a second jab.      
